---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Education Support | Compassion Bridge Initiative Uganda">

<Header />

<section class="hero">
    <div class="overlay">
        <h1>Giving Children the Opportunity to Learn</h1>

        <p>
            Every child deserves the opportunity to stay in school.
            Through the generosity of compassionate individuals,
            organisations and partners, Compassion Bridge Initiative Uganda
            supports vulnerable children with school fees,
            exercise books and other learning materials.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="intro">

<h2>Education Changes Lives</h2>

<p>

Education is one of the strongest tools for breaking the cycle of poverty.
Many children in Kamuli District are unable to remain in school simply because
their families cannot afford school fees or basic scholastic materials.

Compassion Bridge Initiative Uganda works with generous partners to ensure
that vulnerable children receive the support they need to continue their education.

Every notebook, every school fee payment and every smile represents renewed hope
for a brighter future.

</p>

</section>

<section class="impact">

<h2>Our Impact</h2>

<div class="impact-grid">

<div class="card">
<h3>40+</h3>
<p>Children Supported</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>40+</h3>
<p>Families Reached</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>2</h3>
<p>International Partners</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>100%</h3>
<p>Hope Restored</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="gallery">

<h2>Education Support in Action</h2>

<p class="gallery-text">

These photographs capture moments of hope as vulnerable children receive
exercise books, scholastic materials and educational support.

</p>

<div class="gallery-grid">

<img src="/education1.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education2.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education3.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education4.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education5.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education6.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education7.jpg" alt="Education Support">

<img src="/education8.jpg" alt="Education Support">

</div>

</section>

<section class="cta">

<h2>You Can Keep a Child in School</h2>

<p>

Your support provides school fees,
exercise books,
pens,
school supplies
and hope to vulnerable children.

</p>

<a href="/donate" class="donate-btn">Support a Child</a>

</section>

<Footer />

</Layout>

<style>

.hero{

height:70vh;

background:url("/education1.jpg") center center/cover;

display:flex;

align-items:center;

justify-content:center;

}

.overlay{

background:rgba(0,0,0,.55);

padding:60px;

color:white;

text-align:center;

max-width:900px;

border-radius:12px;

}

.overlay h1{

font-size:3rem;

margin-bottom:20px;

}

.overlay p{

font-size:1.2rem;

line-height:1.8;

}

.intro{

padding:80px 10%;

max-width:1000px;

margin:auto;

text-align:center;

}

.intro h2{

color:#0b5e3c;

margin-bottom:20px;

font-size:2.2rem;

}

.intro p{

font-size:1.1rem;

line-height:2;

color:#555;

}

.impact{

background:#f7f9fc;

padding:80px 10%;

text-align:center;

}

.impact-grid{

display:grid;

grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));

gap:30px;

margin-top:50px;

}

.card{

background:white;

padding:35px;

border-radius:12px;

box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);

}

.card h3{

font-size:2.5rem;

color:#0b5e3c;

}

.gallery{

padding:80px 8%;

text-align:center;

}

.gallery-text{

margin-bottom:40px;

color:#666;

}

.gallery-grid{

display:grid;

grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));

gap:20px;

}

.gallery-grid img{

width:100%;

height:260px;

object-fit:cover;

border-radius:10px;

transition:.3s;

}

.gallery-grid img:hover{

transform:scale(1.04);

}

.cta{

padding:80px;

text-align:center;

background:#0b5e3c;

color:white;

}

.donate-btn{

display:inline-block;

margin-top:30px;

padding:15px 40px;

background:#f4b400;

color:black;

font-weight:bold;

border-radius:8px;

text-decoration:none;

}

</style>